   License: Educational Community License 2.0.
   Source:  https://github.com/YalaLab/rave

The teacher wrappers under rate-evals/rate_eval/models/ load externally published
foundation models (CT-CLIP, Curia, Pillar-0, TANGERINE). Those model weights are
not distributed here; obtain them from their respective providers under their own
terms.
